    "body": "Ok so `transformHit` looks good but what about other widgets? `transformFacetValue` `transformData` (stats) `transformXX`?\n\nI like `transformHit` only worried that we will then need a lot of other tokens.\n\nMaybe `transformData` (full data, stats, toggle..) and `transformItems` (any list-based)?\n",
